{"word":"G1807 - ἐξαιρέω - exairéō - ex-ahee-reh'-o - Deliver","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξαιρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exairéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-ahee-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Deliver</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விடுவி, பிடுங்கு, விடுதலையாக்கு"},{"paragraph":"1. to pluck out, draw out"},{"paragraph":"2. to choose out, to rescue, deliver"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G138 - αἱρέομαι - hairéomai - hahee-reh'-om-ahee/138\">G138</a>; active voice to <i>tear out</i>; middle voice to <i>select</i>; figuratively to <i>release:</i> - deliver, pluck out, rescue.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}